{"tid":1737714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有任務畀你啦】打電話，投訴奶共候選人！","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:08:57.000Z","uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27d8207a0575b736d707c3b558679328c245fedc","tid":1737714,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"1. 選舉臨近，係咪見到好多保皇黨、假黃絲、奶共獨立候選人出黎宣傳？<br />\n<br />\n2. 系咪阻街霸路、旗仔/易拉架擺到周圍都係呢？（選管會只批banner掛系特定地點，所有旗仔/易拉架都係違規）、噪音擾民？<br />\n<br />\n3. 睇唔過眼？想投訴？唔使打1823，<br />\n<br />\n打以下直線電話就得，區區都有真人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n4. 請各位返工返學放工放學，打個電話，幫手制裁呢班奶共撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中西區 \t2852 3875<br />\n灣仔區 \t2835 2003<br />\n東區 \t2879 7095<br />\n南區 \t2553 3130<br />\n油尖旺區 \t2399 2753<br />\n深水埗區 \t2150 8207<br />\n九龍城區 \t3575 3958<br />\n黃大仙區 \t3143 1136<br />\n觀塘區 \t2756 0665<br />\n荃灣區 \t3515 5806<br />\n屯門區 \t2940 1755<br />\n元朗區 \t2475 3854<br />\n北區 \t2675 1728<br />\n大埔區 \t3580 2694<br />\n西貢 \t3740 5375<br />\n沙田區 \t2158 5430<br />\n葵青區 \t2426 7173<br />\n離島區 \t2852 4337"},{"pid":"21385a5fbb9aca4f3b963b130236240ffceedf7a","tid":1737714,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"𥄫實你㗎"},{"pid":"72fee6982180e192ad1e62b34799272d28d8ec1d","tid":1737714,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個任務岩晒冷氣軍師做。<br />\n<br />\n齊齊打電話，打到星期日。"},{"pid":"02bd00ee83ef0c547423b00e2bd533dcb2a1b8e1","tid":1737714,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21385a5fbb9aca4f3b963b130236240ffceedf7a","tid":1737714,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"𥄫實你㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"你放心，飯民做錯野，我照樣會屌。"},{"pid":"fc8b99b261101fb559b4a3a0e6fd25067117d7d0","tid":1737714,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:43:50.000Z